detaileddescription.para: A benchmark that evaluates the non-vectorized read and vectorized read with pos-delete in the Spark data source for Iceberg.

This class uses a dataset with a flat schema. To run this benchmark for spark-3.3: ./gradlew -DsparkVersions=3.3 :iceberg-spark:iceberg-spark-3.3:jmh -PjmhIncludeRegex=IcebergSourceParquetWithUnrelatedDeleteBenchmark -PjmhOutputPath=benchmark/iceberg-source-parquet-with-unrelated-delete-benchmark-result.txt
